      "text": "Webhook — Evolution API (WhatsApp)\n\nPOST  /webhook/:sellerId\n\n  → Recebe mensagens do WhatsApp\n  → Transcreve audio (Whisper) e imagem (GPT-4o)\n  → Acumula no Redis (janela de 5s)\n  → Publica job no RabbitMQ",
