    {
      "id": "agent_text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 595,
      "y": 855,
      "width": 470,
      "height": 180,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#7048e8",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 301,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 401,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1711000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Agente de IA (interno — consumido via RabbitMQ)\nNao exposto via REST — processamento assincrono\n\nFerramentas:\n  • rag-search         → Busca vetorial no Pinecone\n  • think              → Raciocinio SPIN Selling\n  • classify-lead      → Qualificacao silenciosa do lead\n  • check-availability → Verifica agenda Google Calendar\n  • schedule-meeting   → Cria reuniao + link Google Meet\n\nModelo: DeepSeek v3 (OpenRouter) | Memoria: Redis (200 msgs)",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "agent_box",
      "originalText": "Agente de IA (interno — consumido via RabbitMQ)\nNao exposto via REST — processamento assincrono\n\nFerramentas:\n  • rag-search         → Busca vetorial no Pinecone\n  • think              → Raciocinio SPIN Selling\n  • classify-lead      → Qualificacao silenciosa do lead\n  • check-availability → Verifica agenda Google Calendar\n  • schedule-meeting   → Cria reuniao + link Google Meet\n\nModelo: DeepSeek v3 (OpenRouter) | Memoria: Redis (200 msgs)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

    {
      "id": "middleware_box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 580,
      "y": 75,
      "width": 500,
