    },
    {
      "id": "middleware_text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 595,
      "y": 85,
      "width": 470,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 311,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 411,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1711000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Middlewares, Validacao e Modelo de Dados\n\nAutenticacao:\n  • clerkMiddleware()  → Aplicado globalmente\n  • requireApiAuth     → Exigido nas rotas protegidas\n  • Webhook bypassed   → /webhook (Evolution API)\n\nValidacao:\n  • validate(zodSchema)  → Valida body da request\n  • uuidParam('id')      → Valida parametros UUID\n\nModelo de dados (PostgreSQL + TypeORM):\n  Company  → has many Sellers (criados via seed)\n  Seller   → has many Leads\n  Seller   → has Pinecone namespace (documentos RAG)\n  Lead     → vinculado por remoteJid (contato WhatsApp)\n  Lead     → classificado pelo agente (temperatura, objecoes...)",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "middleware_box",
      "originalText": "Middlewares, Validacao e Modelo de Dados\n\nAutenticacao:\n  • clerkMiddleware()  → Aplicado globalmente\n  • requireApiAuth     → Exigido nas rotas protegidas\n  • Webhook bypassed   → /webhook (Evolution API)\n\nValidacao:\n  • validate(zodSchema)  → Valida body da request\n  • uuidParam('id')      → Valida parametros UUID\n\nModelo de dados (PostgreSQL + TypeORM):\n  Company  → has many Sellers (criados via seed)\n  Seller   → has many Leads\n  Seller   → has Pinecone namespace (documentos RAG)\n  Lead     → vinculado por remoteJid (contato WhatsApp)\n  Lead     → classificado pelo agente (temperatura, objecoes...)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

